dct_title_s: Carte particuliere de l'Isle de Juan Fernandés : tirée du Voyage de l'Amiral Anson
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by soundings. Probably issued in: Histoire générale des voyages ... Paris : Didot, 1746-1789. In lower margin: Tome XI in 4⁰. No. 6. Tome 16 in 8⁰. Page 285. At top of plate: Vüe de l'sle de Juan Fernandés. Venant du côté de l'Est Nord Est.
